OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start but cloud
OL,6,Fwill gradually thin and break up,
OL,7,Fallowing some bright or sunny spells
OL,8,Fto develop. The best of the sunshine
OL,9,Fwill be in the east and in any
OL,10,Fsunshine it will feel mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud and patchy rain may
OL,13,Fmove into the far west at times
OL,14,Fovernight. Otherwise dry with clear
OL,15,Fspells, but some mist and fog patches
OL,16,Fmay develop, especially in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
