OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FThe far west continuing to
OL,6,Fsee some cloud and patchy rain at
OL,7,Ftimes. Elsewhere, any mist and fog
OL,8,Fclearing allowing some bright or sunny
OL,9,Fspells to develop. Feeling very mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,12,Fmoving across the region on Thursday
OL,13,Fbefore turning brighter with some
OL,14,Fshowers on Friday. Further rain likely
OL,15,Flater on Saturday. Temperatures
OL,16,Freturning to nearer average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
